@startuml
title StatSync - Event Logging Sequence

actor Manager
participant "Expo Client" as Client
participant "Django REST API" as Django
database "PostgreSQL" as PG
queue "Redis" as Redis
participant "Node WS Server" as NodeWS
participant "Connected Clients" as Clients

Manager -> Client : Select player + event
Client -> Django : POST increment endpoint (JWT)
Django -> PG : Update PlayerEventStat
Django -> PG : Insert PlayerEventInstance
Django -> Redis : Publish match_event
Redis -> NodeWS : Deliver message
NodeWS -> Clients : Broadcast via WebSocket
Clients -> Clients : Update UI

@enduml
